\" --- Lists ---
.de *
.   IP \(bu 2
\\$1
..
.de +
.   IP \(bu 2
\\$1
..
.de -
.   IP \(bu 2
\\$1
..

\" --- Block quotes ---
.de >
.   QP
.   I
.   ad b
..

\" --- Horizontal rule ---
.de ---
\l'\\n(.lu\(ul'
..
